Pre-Game Insights: The San Francisco Giants and Milwaukee Brewers are set to face off on August 29, 2024.
Aaron Civale will start for the Milwaukee Brewers, while Hayden Birdsong will start for the San Francisco Giants.
The betting odds for the game are Milwaukee Brewers -139 and San Francisco Giants +118.
Others: The game will be broadcast on BALLY and NBCSN.
The series is the final installment in a three-game series.
The Giants took the first game of the series, while the Brewers won the second game.
